response.overview: The visual work of Cinco seis veinte responds to a training of bodies. Specifically a visual entertainment of a generative model of images with artificial intelligence. The human body is re-imagined by an algorithm, fueled by a mix of digitized fragments from radiographs, tomographies, electronic boards, wraps and cables. The result is a journey into the formation and at the same time dissection of this new organism, as if it imploded into thousands of pieces, being able to visualize segments or frames of the hybrid nature of its constitution.
response.title: Cinco seis veinte
